		"npc_citizen.question01" = "I don't think this war's ever gonna end. "
		"npc_citizen.question02" = " "
		"npc_citizen.question03" = "I don't dream anymore. "
		"npc_citizen.question04" = "When this is all over I'm...aw, who am I kidding? "
		"npc_citizen.question05" = "Whoa...deja vu!"
		"npc_citizen.question06" = " "
		"npc_citizen.question07" = "You smell that? It's freedom. "
		"npc_citizen.question08" = "If I ever get my hands on Dr. Breen..."
		"npc_citizen.question09" = "I could eat a horse, hooves and all. "
		"npc_citizen.question10" = "I can't believe this day has finally come. "
		"npc_citizen.question11" = "I'm pretty sure this isn't part of the plan. "
		"npc_citizen.question12" = "Looks to me like things are getting worse, not better. "
		"npc_citizen.question13" = "If I could live my life over again "
		"npc_citizen.question14" = "I'm not even gonna tell you what that reminds me of. "
		"npc_citizen.question15" = "They're never gonna make a stalker out of me. "
		"npc_citizen.question16" = "Finally, change is in the air! "
		"npc_citizen.question17" = "Do you feel it? I feel it! "
		"npc_citizen.question18" = "I don't feel anything anymore. "
		"npc_citizen.question19" = "I can't remember the last time I had a shower. "
		"npc_citizen.question20" = "Some day this will all be a bad memory. "
		"npc_citizen.question21" = "I'm not a betting man, but the odds are not good. "
		"npc_citizen.question22" = "Doesn't anyone care what I think? "
		"npc_citizen.question23" = "I can't get this tune out of my head.  [whistles]"
		"npc_citizen.question24" = "I do not want to know what kind of meat this is. "
		"npc_citizen.question25" = "I just knew it was gonna be one of those days. "
		"npc_citizen.question26" = "This is bullshit!"
		"npc_citizen.question27" = "I think I ate something bad."
		"npc_citizen.question28" = "God I'm hungry."
		"npc_citizen.question29" = "When this is all over, I'm gonna mate. "
		"npc_citizen.question30" = "I'm glad there's no kids around to see this "
		"npc_citizen.question31" = "I can't remember the last time I had, well, anything. "
